The back-end electronics is located in a counting room approximately 100 m away from the ATLAS detector. The data acquisition system of the Tile Calorimeter is split into four partitions, the ATLAS A-side (η>0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
